title: Nomination and Withdrawal Sent to the Senate | The White House
content: NOMINATION SENT TO THE SENATE:     Ronald T. Keohane, of New York, to be an Assistant Secretary of Defense, vice James N. Stewart.WITHDRAWAL SENT TO THE SENATE:     Brenda Sue Fulton, of New Jersey, to be an Assistant Secretary of Defense, vice James N. Stewart, which was sent to the Senate on January 4, 2022.###
